## Accessibility Guidelines

- Maintain color contrast ratio of at least 4.5:1 for normal text
- Focus states must be visible for keyboard navigation
- Interactive elements should have minimum size of 44x44px
- Text should remain readable at minimum 16px for body text
- Include hover and focus states for all interactive elements
- Support keyboard navigation throughout the application

## Implementation Notes

- Use CSS variables for consistent theme application
- Components should be responsive by default
- Maintain backward compatibility when updating the design system
- Use semantic HTML and ARIA attributes where appropriate
- Document any component variations not covered in the core design system 